com.epoch.energyDiagrams

Class OED

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.energyDiagrams.EDiagram
      • com.epoch.energyDiagrams.OED
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CellsLineConstants, DiagramCellConstants, EDiagramConstants, EnergyQDatumConstants, OEDConstants

    public class OED
extends EDiagram
implements CellsLineConstants, OEDConstants
    A diagram correlating the energies and occupancies of atomic and molecular orbitals. Consists of a table, each cell of which may contain one or more orbitals, each of which has an occupancy.
